    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it would benefit from a tune-up and some suspension work in the near future. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and fading clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the air conditioning is currently blowing cool but not cold. It is a functional vehicle with plenty of life left, provided the new owner addresses its minor maintenance needs.",
      "price": 19500.0,
