    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain exhibits excellent synchro engagement and a crisp clutch take-up. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle valve actuators, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains robust. The exterior retains a deep luster, while the Novillo leather interior shows only minor bolstering wear consistent with a well-cared-for enthusiast vehicle. The hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback, and the braking system retains strong initial bite with no signs of rotor warping.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of performance and daily reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by clean alloy wheels; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular road use, the body remains straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership. The leather upholstery is supple and clean, featuring only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the interior has remained strictly smoke-free. All electronic components, including the premium audio system, navigation, and heated seats, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent fluid service and multi-point inspection just completed. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. This car is ready for its next chapter and offers a high-quality driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. Service records are available upon request.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This specimen has been curated for the discerning driver who values a documented service history and consistent performance. The exterior retains a professional finish, complemented by an interior environment that remains both clean and highly functional. Offering a refined balance of durability and prestige, this automobile stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains prepared for immediate, reliable service.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and is ready to hit the road whenever you are! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
