      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec BMW E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically sorted, having received a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The 6-speed Getrag transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power distribution. The suspension is tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers, while the braking system maintains excellent bite with cross-drilled rotors. While the finish shows minor road patina, the drivetrain performance is sharp and consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle.",
